Products.RichDescription: Organic silverbeet, also called swiss chard is often used in mediterranean cooking. An earthy tasting green. Wash in cold salted water and drain, then shred and add raw to salads. Alternatively, slice and use in stir-fries, curries, quiches, soups or as part of a side dish. Cook silverbeet as briefly as possible to retain maximum nutrient content.
